posts.title: I am not an emotional Man, but the shit going on right now is painful.
posts.content:
I feel immense empathy for those whose lives have been completly obliterated in the wake of the hurricane. To hear those stories makes me fucking weep, and I don't fucking cry over much. To hear about those who've gone in on their own dime to bring aid, to bring Starlinks, to bring help, only to hear about slashed tires, FEMA preventing them from giving out aid, flying their helicopters in to rescue, or drones to find people... IT PISSES ME OFF WITH SUCH IMMENSE FUCKING ANGER!

I know there is cowardice in Mankind. I know there is idiocy in Mankind. I know there is corruption in Mankind... And I also know there is more in Mankind. There is potential, and there is wonderous beauty in Mankind, and the light in the world is rare, and it fights against the darkness constantly, and right now to see the corrupt stop the light from helping, the idiots who enable it, and the cowards who fucking do nothing... Just rage and tears is what I feel. Rage and tears.

We are Americans. We need to become AMERICA again. Even if we get Trump back in we CANNOT STOP BEING VIGILANT! WE NEED TO HOLD EVERYONE ACCOUNTABLE TO JUSTICE, REAL JUSTICE! We need to never stop. Those responsible, in any capacity, in destroying this country from within needs to be held accountable. Accountable for TREASON!

NEVER AGAIN SHOULD ANY AMERICAN SUFFER FROM TRAITORS. NEVER AGAIN SHOULD THOSE AMERICANS WHO NEED HELP BE FORGOTTEN, DENIED, OR THREATENED.

I don't give a single fuck about any other country. I don't want a single fucking dime to go to another country. I don't want a single fucking immigrant to cross our borders. AMERICA FIRST, and AMERICANS FIRST!

My heart goes out to those hurting. To those who lost their homes, their community, their family... I don't fucking cry, but I got tears in my eyes right now thinking about you all.
